{
  "stem": "3165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, we can-- and they left our village, so we can go back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back to the house, and of course, they were all frightened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- being a child, again, I was running, and I did what my parents asked me to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was happening several times like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The neighbors would come in and say Gestapos are-- this neighbor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're looking for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also Ukrainian [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were collaborating with the Germans, and I guess they had an agreement that the Ukrainians will help the Germans to find all the Jewish people, because they knew exactly where the Jewish people were living-- which homes, which cities, which towns, which villages.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're going to help the Germans to to catch all the-- get all the Jewish people and kill them as well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so now we have to be careful of the Ukrainians, as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this hiding, running away from the house, running into the fields, you know, happened a few times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, one morning, we were all home and we heard storming in into our house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The doors were open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Gestapos came right-- walked right in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were maybe four or five of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they saw my-- all of us, and they said, OK, all you men, you got to come forward.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they grabbed my father and my two other brothers, and my youngest brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was maybe 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he ran up to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took her around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, oh, Mom, I'm so scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are they taking me?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
